[package]
name = "udisks2"
version = "0.2.0"
edition = "2021"
rust-version = "1.75"
description = " Unofficial crate for interacting with the UDisks2 API"
readme = "README.md"
license = "LGPL-2.1"
repository = "https://github.com/FineFindus/udisks-rs"
keywords = [ "udisks", "udisks2", "manipulating-disk", "storage",]
categories = [ "api-bindings", "hardware-support", "os::linux-apis",]

[dependencies]
zbus = "4.0.0"
serde_repr = "0.1.18"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "derive",]

[dependencies.enumflags2]
version = "0.7.9"
features = [ "serde",]

[dependencies.gettext-rs]
version = "0.7"
features = [ "gettext-system",]

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.36"
features = [ "full",]
